animation.human: Camera starts with a medium shot of the iceberg's tip above the waterline, slowly pushing in. The iceberg emits a rhythmic pulsating glow that intensifies in waves across its surface. As the camera continues its forward dolly movement, a bright flash of light blooms from the center of the frame, creating a transition effect. The camera then tilts down and pushes through the waterline, revealing the massive submerged portion of the iceberg below. The pulsating glow effect carries through both sections, with the flash serving as the punctuation between above and below water environments. Smooth, continuous camera movement with dynamic lighting transition.
